wiki.content:
This TEED track is the second single from the UK artists 2012 album, Trouble. The single chronologically succeeded "Trouble" and preceded "You Need Me On My Own". The song was written by TEED and self-produced under the same name. As well as TEED's own it features vocals by Luisa from Lulu and the Lampshades. The song was recently featured on a line of advertisements for Nokia's Lumia.
